<div class="node--body">
<div class="node--featured-item__title"><a class="" data-hide-link-title="0" data-icon-position="" href="https://www.pnas.org/content/116/7/2400">Opinion: “Plan S” falls short for society publishers—and for the researchers they serve</a></div>
